WEBVTT

00:00:27.183 --> 00:00:30.142
Eu miraba o teléfono.
Pensei que podería eliminalo.

00:00:30.442 --> 00:00:34.607
Ou podería facer o que penso
que todos quixemos facer sempre.

00:00:34.631 --> 00:00:36.152
(Risos)

00:00:38.251 --> 00:00:41.190
E dixen "Solomon,
o teu correo intrígame."

00:00:41.190 --> 00:00:43.476
(Risos)

00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:48.476
(Aplausos)

00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:50.920
E o xogo púxose en marcha.

00:00:53.214 --> 00:00:56.175
Dixo "Querido James Veitch,
Imos enviarche Ouro."


00:00:56.199 --> 00:00:57.896
(Risos)

00:00:58.302 --> 00:01:01.199
"Vas gañar un 10 %
do ouro que distribúe."